{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Tree shaking","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Tree_shaking","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>Tree shaking</strong> 是一个通常用于描述移除 JavaScript 上下文中的未引用代码 (dead-code) 行为的术语。</p>\n<p>它依赖于 ES2015 中的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/import\">import</a> 和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/export\">export</a> 语句，用来检测代码模块是否被导出、导入，且被 JavaScript 文件使用。</p>\n<p>在现代 JavaScript 应用程序中，我们使用模块打包 (如<a href=\"https://webpack.js.org/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">webpack</a>或<a href=\"https://github.com/rollup/rollup\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Rollup</a>) 将多个 JavaScript 文件打包为单个文件时自动删除未引用的代码。这对于准备预备发布代码的工作非常重要，这样可以使最终文件具有简洁的结构和最小化大小。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":"<h4 id=\"常识\">常识</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://exploringjs.com/es6/ch_modules.html#_benefit-dead-code-elimination-during-bundling\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">\"捆绑过程中死代码消除的好处\"</a> 在 Axel Rauschmayer 的书中:“探索 JS:模块”</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"技术参数资料\">技术参数资料</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://webpack.js.org/guides/tree-shaking/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">用 webpack 实现 Tree shaking</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"Tree shaking 是一个通常用于描述移除 JavaScript 上下文中的未引用代码 (dead-code) 行为的术语。","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Tree shaking","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Tree shaking","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Tree shaking","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/tree_shaking","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/tree_shaking/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374